Clarence David Moore escaped from a North Carolina prison in June 1972 . 
  Moore was 23 years old and serving a 10-year sentence for larceny when he escaped . 
  Moore called the Franklin County Sheriff's Office in Kentucky on Monday and admitted to being a fugitive . 
  Moore suffers from several medical conditions and cannot walk . 
  He has not been able to get medical treatment because he does not have a Social Security card . 
  Moore escaped the Polk Youth Institute in Butner, North Carolina . 
 